law.text:
It is the purpose of this subtitle:
To offer incentives and opportunities for creative public and private partnerships within the marketplace to develop state-of-the-art educational technology products and services that promote the use of advanced technologies in the classroom;
To avoid duplication and the development of incompatible systems by strengthening and building upon existing telecommunications infrastructure dedicated to educational purposes;
To provide Maryland public school students with equal opportunities to develop a strong academic foundation;
To facilitate expanded educational choices not otherwise available to Maryland public school students through on-line courses and services; and
To expand professional development opportunities available to educational staff in Maryland public schools through on-line courses and services.
